Conway Invaders
"The most awesome crappy space invaders knockoff evar. Fer serious."

Source code is in the src/ directory. There is a makefile there. Nothing should
be required besides OpenGL and GLUT.

Build Instructions

Linux (Debian and similar):

    sudo apt-get install freeglut3-dev
    cd src
    make

Mac (must have XCode installed):

    cd src
    make
